sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Student Browser
    participant F as Frontend Home.jsx
    participant A as Express API
    participant P as Portal Scraper
    participant DB as SQL Server

    U->>F: Enter universityId + password
    F->>A: POST /api/auth/login
    A->>P: verifyCredentials Playwright
    P->>P: Login to ums.mu.edu.lb
    P-->>A: valid + studentName
    A->>DB: Upsert Users + PortalCredentials
    A->>DB: Sync AcademicHistory
    A-->>F: JWT token + user object
    F->>F: Store mugate_token in localStorage
    F-->>U: Logged-in navigation
